/wiki/wikcnIDqFcfRLvINChAn8jIvv0b#).\n\nIf the faas idc which you are using does not support ,see [Currently faas IDC does not support](#Currently-faas-IDC-does-not-support).\n\n### Currently faas IDC does not support\n\nYou can choose one way to solve:\n\n1. Initiate a merge request, the address is [https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/merge_requests](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/merge_requests), the file is [packages/fetch-protocol-faas/src/consts.ts](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/tree/master/packages/fetch-protocol-faas/src/consts.ts).\n\n2. Initiate a issue , address is [https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/issues](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/issues).\n\n3. Directly Use faas domain name to initiate request(In this time the request is the same as the general request).\n\n```ts\nawait fetch('faas://vqyvl29t.fn-boe.bytedance.net/xxx');\n```\n","repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service"},"scripts":{"prepublish":"npm run build","test":"ROUTE_IP=10.225.130.44 RUNTIME_IDC_NAME=boe ../../node_modules/.bin/jest --config ./jest.config.json --coverage --env=node","build":"rm -rf lib && ../../node_modules/.bin/tsc"},"_npmUser":{"name":"nodejs-team","email":"nodejs-team@bytedance.com"},"_npmVersion":"lerna/undefined/node@v14.20.1+x64 (linux)","dependencies":{"@byted-service/consul":"^2.1.3","@byted-service/env":"^1.12.2","@byted-service/fetch-core":"^2.4.0","@byted-service/logger":"^2.1.2","tslib":"^1.9.3"},"engines":{"node":">=10.0.0"},"main":"lib/index.js","name":"@byted-service/fetch-protocol-faas","types":"lib/index.d.ts"},"2.3.3-alpha.0":{"gitHead":"8647a12549292b5c5b54befe2dae3d52bcac3e71","main":"lib/index.js","readme":"# @byted-service/fetch-protocol-faas\n\n[![bnpm](https://web-bnpm.byted.org/badge/v/@byted-service/fetch-protocol-faas.svg?style=flat-square)](https://web-bnpm.byted.org/package/@byted-service/fetch-protocol-faas) [![download](https://2y8ngapf.fn.bytedance.ne